dct_title_s: Het beloofde Landt Canaan door wandelt van onsen Salichmaecker Iesu Christo neffens syne Apostelen
dct_description_sm: door Nicolaes Visscher; C.I. Visscher excud., Broeck sculp.
2 bar scales on map, given in "Duytsche Mylen" and "Uren gaens".
North oriented toward upper right of sheet.
Key in banner in upper left.
Decorative cartouches, compass rose, cherubs, figures, buildings, ships.
Pictorial vignettes at bottom, showing biblical scenes.
"Dese Caerte wert gestelt voor het Evangelium Matthei."
dct_creator_sm: Broeck, Abraham van den, approximately 1616 or 1617-1688
